    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><rs key="#Testamentum">Testamentum</rs> factum per <persName
                            key="#childOf #marriage #parentOf #Testamentum #Breve/memoratorium"
                                ><name ref="Gherardus/Boreli">Gerardum Boreli</name></persName> de
                        uno <rs key="#Mansi">manso</rs> terre posito in loco qui dicitur
                            <placeName>Corte</placeName> et unum in loco qui dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/2416">Canule</placeName>. Numero VI. In nomine domini
                        nostri Yhesu Christi. <rs key="#Breve/memoratorium">Brevis recordationis
                            cartula</rs> future recordationis causa, qualiter <persName
                            key="#Breve/memoratorium #childOf #marriage #parentOf"><name
                                ref="Gherardus/f. Borelli">Girardus</name></persName><persName
                            key="#parentOf"><name ref="Borellus  ">Borelli</name></persName> quondam
                            <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs> in sua ultima disposuit voluntate.
                        Presentibus pluribus hominibus ibique astantibus, dixit atque firmavit
                            <persName key="#marriage"><name ref="Matilda"
                            >Mathildam</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#marriage">uxorem</rs> suam usumfructum habere omnium suarum rerum
                        mobilium et immobilium seu familiis quandiu vixerit vel si secundas non
                        contraxerit nuptias. Duas filias suas, scilicet <persName key="#childOf"
                                ><name ref="Gerburga">Girburga</name></persName> seu <persName
                            key="#childOf"><name ref="Berta">Berta</name></persName>, proprietatem
                        predictarum rerum posite infra <rs key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/161"><placeName key="#Comitatus"
                                ref="#places/53">Parmensis</placeName></geogName> vel <geogName
                            key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/193"><placeName key="#Comitatus"
                                ref="#places/191">Regensi</placeName></geogName> atque <geogName
                            key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/124"><placeName key="#Comitatus"
                                ref="#places/59">Veronensi</placeName></geogName>, eo vero tenore ut
                        si liberis hominibus se copulaverint et filios ex legiptimo matrimonio
                        habueirint et si servis vel libertinis seu familiis se coniunxerint non
                        amplius ex mea substantia habeant unaqueque nisi mansum unum, scilicet
                        Girburga mansum quem <rs key="#Agricultural_workers">rectum et laboratum seu
                            detentum</rs> est per <persName key="#Agricultural_workers"><name
                                ref="Stephanus/Scurtagata">Stephanum Scurtagata</name></persName> in
                        loco qui dicitur Corte, Berte vero habeat mansum unum que detentum est per
                            <persName key="#Agricultural_workers #siblingOf"><name ref="Benedictus"
                                >Benedictum</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Agricultural_workers #siblingOf"><name ref="Ioahnnes"
                                >Iohannem</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">germanos</rs> in corte Canule. Et si hoc evenerit ut
                        predicte filie sine legiptimis filiis ut supra legitur mortue fuerint,
                        suprascripte res <rs key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">proprietario
                            iure</rs> deveniant ad <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Testamentum #Breve/memoratorium #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti Benedicti et Sancti
                            Simeonis</orgName>, exceptis infrascriptis mansis. Et si una ex sine
                        herede mortua fuerit, pars ipsius non ad sororem sed ad predictum
                        monasterium deveniat. Et insuper liceat Mathilde uxori mee una cum <persName
                            key="#Witness #Testamentum #Breve/memoratorium #Priests #childOf"><name
                                ref="Wido/presbiter">Vuido</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> filio quondam <persName key="parentOf"
                                ><name ref="Teuperga/de Monteclo">Teuperge</name></persName> de loco
                            <placeName ref="#places/2410">Monteclo</placeName> ex ipsis rebus
                        vendere si debitum ei apparverit quod aliter persolvere non potuerit. Actum
                        est hoc in loco suprascripto <placeName ref="#places/4413">Sancti
                            Benedicti</placeName>. Anni Domini millesimo septuagesimo sexto, septimo
                        idus februarii, indictione quartadecima. + Ego Vuido presbiter prepositus
                        manu mea firmavi. (S.) Ego <persName
                            key="#Witness #Testamentum #Breve/memoratorium #Judge"><name
                                ref="Maginfredus/iudex">Malnfredus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> interfui. (S.) Ego <persName
                            key="#Witness #Testamentum #Breve/memoratorium"><name
                                ref="Iohannes/legis doctor">Iohannes</name></persName>
                        <rs>legis doctor</rs> interfui. Omnia autem ut supra legitur acta sunt <rs
                            key="#Witness">in presentia</rs>
                        <persName key="#Witness #Testamentum #Breve/memoratorium #childOf"><name
                                ref="Atto/f. Uberici">Attonis</name></persName> filii <persName
                            key="#parentOf"><name ref="Ubericus">Uberici</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness #Testamentum #Breve/memoratorium"><name
                                ref="Bezo/de Corte Nova">Bezonis</name></persName> de <placeName
                            ref="#places/2996">Corte Nova</placeName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Testamentum #Breve/memoratorium"><name ref="Raginbaldus"
                                >Rambaldi</name></persName> seu <persName
                            key="#Witness #Testamentum #Breve/memoratorium"><name ref="Vuibertus"
                                >Vuiberti</name></persName> atque <persName
                            key="#Witness #Testamentum #Breve/memoratorium"><name ref="Rigerius"
                                >Rigerii</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Testamentum #Breve/memoratorium"><name
                                ref="Vuibertus/de Bibianello">Vuiberti</name></persName> da
                            <placeName ref="#places/2468">Bibianello</placeName> etiam <persName
                            key="#Witness #Testamentum #Breve/memoratorium"><name
                                ref="Bernardus/de Burbasio">Barnardo</name></persName> da <placeName
                            ref="#places/482">Burbasio</placeName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Testamentum #Breve/memoratorium"><name ref="Albitius"
                                >Albizio</name></persName> atque <persName
                            key="#Witness #Testamentum #Breve/memoratorium"><name ref="Turisendus"
                                >Turisindo</name></persName> namque <persName
                            key="#Witness #Testamentum #Breve/memoratorium"><name
                                ref="Wilibertus de Gosberto">Vilbertus</name></persName> de
                            <persName><name
                                ref="Gausbertus">Gosberto</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Testamentum #Breve/memoratorium"><name
                                ref="Iohannes/de Ingezo">Iohannis</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name ref="Ingitius">Ingezo</name></persName>. Ego
                            <persName key="#Notary #Testamentum #Breve/memoratorium #Writer"><name
                                ref="Iohannes/notarius">Iohannes</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> duas cartas in uno tenore <rs key="#Writer"
                            >conscripsi</rs>. </ab>
                </div>
